# ``musiccloud``

A macOS menu bar application that automatically converts music streaming URLs to universal short links.

## Overview

musiccloud monitors your clipboard for music streaming URLs from services like Spotify, Apple Music, YouTube Music, and more. When it detects a URL, it automatically converts it to a short musiccloud.io link that works across all platforms.

### Features

- **Automatic Clipboard Monitoring**: Continuously watches for streaming URLs
- **Multi-Service Support**: Works with Spotify, Apple Music, YouTube Music, Tidal, Deezer, and 20+ services
- **Universal Links**: Creates short URLs that work on any platform
- **Rich Metadata**: Downloads artwork and track/album/artist information
- **Conversion History**: Keeps track of all converted URLs
- **Menu Bar Integration**: Quick access from the macOS menu bar

